name: INTENSE ENGINE BUZZSAW | Air Canada Airbus A321-200 Takeoff from Calgary Airport
description:
I've been focusing more on my trip reports lately instead of dedicated takeoff/landing videos like this one, but I think the engine sound from this departure was too good to not post as its own video! Here we have C-FLKX, an Airbus A321-200, operating Air Canada flight 140 to Toronto spooling up and taking off from Calgary International Airport in July 2018. Hope you enjoy this engine buzzsaw as much as I did filming it!

Thanks for watching!
